rows.label: qst703101_msg0003
rows.name:
If not deliver quickly, partner sure
to flip lid...

rows.label: qst703101_msg0005
rows.name: Please to listen to Dudan's woes!

rows.label: qst703101_msg0006
rows.name:
Dudan is salvager by trade, as friends
see. Is entire livelihood.

rows.label: qst703101_msg0007
rows.name:
Dudan been diving off Lasqam Cove
with Wood Cylinders in effort to find
specific treasure.

rows.label: qst703101_msg0008
rows.name:
But all Dudan find is useless
collectibles, value of scrap. More
worth to throw away than keep!

rows.label: qst703101_msg0009
rows.name:
Probably fault of Wood Cylinders.
Not really built to last.

rows.label: qst703101_msg0010
rows.name:
Have heard salvagers in Superbia use shiny Silver Cylinders
or somesuch.

rows.label: qst703101_msg0011
rows.name:
Dudan not have luxury to use such
high-tech equipment, but want to
change that!

rows.label: qst703101_msg0012
rows.name:
It maybe asking too much, but could
Dudan trouble travelers for helping?

rows.label: qst703101_msg0013
rows.name:
Would need friends to collect Apple
Lamps and Alloy Sheeting.

rows.label: qst703101_msg0014
rows.name:
Then Dudan can dive deep into Cloud
Sea with Silver Cylinder on back and
glide to treasure like sleeky Serprond!

rows.label: qst703101_msg0015
rows.name:
If friends do this, will give all of leftover
useless... Ah, no, sorry, mean very very
precious Bat Hinges as reward!
